{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ListProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ListProtocol\/append(data:)"},"abstract":[{"text":"Adds a new element on to the end of the list.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/listprotocol\/append(data:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"append","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV","text":"ListRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:4GLib12ListProtocolPAAE6append4dataAA0B3RefVSgSvSg_tF","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"append(data:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"append"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) -> "},{"text":"ListRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib7ListRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ListRef"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that the return value is the new start of the list,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"